#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>SFTP</acronym> is a Secure file transfer protocol. <command>sftp</"
"command> is an interactive file transfer program, similar to ftp, but it "
"performs all operations over an encrypted <command>ssh</command> transport. "
"It may use many of the features of <command>ssh</command>, including public "
"key authentication and compression."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>SFTP</acronym> je varen prenosni protokol za datoteke (Secure File "
"Transfer Protocol). <command>sftp</command> je interaktivni prenosniški "
"program, soroden ftp, vendar pa izvaja vse operacije preko šifriranega "
"prenosa <command>ssh</command>. Lahko uporablja mnogo funkcij <command>ssh</"
"command>, vključno z avtentikacijo z javnimi ključi in stiskanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/sftp\">sftp</ulink>."
msgstr "Oglejte si priročnik: <ulink url=\"man:/sftp\">sftp</ulink>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "SFTP is a simple file transfer protocol. It fills the need of people "
#~ "wanting a protocol that is more useful than TFTP but easier to implement "
#~ "(and less powerful) than FTP. SFTP supports user access control, file "
#~ "transfers, directory listing, directory changing, file renaming and "
#~ "deleting"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "SFTF je preprost protokol za prenos datotek. Izpolnjuje potrebe ljudi ki "
#~ "Ĺželijo bolj uporaben protokol, kot je TFTF a preprostejĹĄi za izvedbo "
#~ "(in manj zmogljiv) kot FTP. SFTP podpira nadzor nad dostopom uporabnikov, "
#~ "prenose datotek, izpis imenikov, njihovo spreminjanje, preimenovanje "
#~ "datotek in brisanje."
